        <div class="container">
            <h2><span id="applyHouse"></span>
            <span>When you're ready to apply</span></h2>
            <p class="subintro">You can apply for your Northern Rock mortgage over the phone on <span class="contactNumber">0800 0285 277*</span>
            or in your local <a class="contenttool" href="/Mortgages/Tools/Branch-Finder">branch</a>.  The application process will take around 30-40 minutes and one of our mortgage advisors will guide you
            through the process to make it as smooth as possible.</p>
     
            <div class="g3 alpha features applyList applyListLeft">
                <h3>What you'll need:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Address(es) for last 3 years</li>
                    <li>Your income</li>
                    <li>Details of your outgoings</li>
                    <li>Details of the mortgages you require</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="g3 omega features applyList">
                <h3>What you'll get:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>A 
<em class="glossary" title="A KFI is a document provided by the mortgage lender, in a standard format, so that you can compare the service, product and offer that they are providing.">KFI (Key Facts Illustration)<span>?</span></em></li>
                    <li>A 
<em class="glossary" title="Also referred to as an Application in Principle, this informs the borrower if, in principle, a lender will provide the money and what amount.">Decision in Principle (DIP)<span>?</span></em></li>
                    <li>Complete your mortgage application</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="pinkButtonBox">
